            </details>

            <details class="group bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-xl cursor-pointer">
              <summary
                class="font-bold text-slate-700 list-none flex justify-between items-center"
              >
                What is the cancellation policy?
                <span
                  class="transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform"
                  >‚ñº</span
                >
              </summary>
              <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2 text-sm">
